As my basecolor I'm using OPI Did You Ear About Van Gogh?

00:00:41.320 --> 00:00:45.360
I think this polish looks perfect as the base color for his manicure

00:00:45.360 --> 00:00:49.120
but a dusty light green would also look really good

00:00:51.450 --> 00:00:54.630
This polish needs two layers to be fully
opaque

00:00:55.430 --> 00:00:59.770
When I'm done I'm going to wait a little while till my basecolor is totally dry

00:01:01.780 --> 00:01:07.560
The next one is from the Deborah Milano Pret a Porter collection and it's number 51 Khaki Green

00:01:08.080 --> 00:01:11.140
Take your dotting tool and start making the first spots

00:01:13.120 --> 00:01:19.160
You can make a couple of small spots or a few bigger ones, that's up to you what you think looks best

00:01:38.100 --> 00:01:40.700
This is OPI A Taupe The Space Needle

00:01:41.500 --> 00:01:45.240
Now we're going to do the exact same
thing as the previous color

00:01:46.720 --> 00:01:51.540
