00:02:04.660 --> 00:02:06.360
This is Green Generation

00:02:07.080 --> 00:02:13.780
Don't just place the colors next to each other, also apply one color over the other to make the design look better

00:02:14.440 --> 00:02:20.320
Make sure that you don't apply a light color over a really dark color because the color can change

00:02:20.320 --> 00:02:25.980
If you don't know if you can layer some color try them on a piece of paper first to see the result

00:02:26.380 --> 00:02:30.900
Now it's time to add some black and I'm using number 71 Total Black

00:02:31.340 --> 00:02:33.860
This is the last color I'm going to use

00:02:37.720 --> 00:02:40.120
Freehand nail art always looks really lumpy

00:02:40.120 --> 00:02:43.700
but when you apply the topcoat everything looks smooth again

00:02:55.709 --> 00:02:59.929
I'm using my eyeliner brush and acetone to clean up the mess I made

00:03:05.310 --> 00:03:11.010
